<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> خ <span class="c2">(٣٨١٣)</span> , م <span class="c2">(٧/ ١٦١ ـ ١٦٢)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> الصَّوَابُ <span class="c2">(فَزَجَلَ)</span> وَالسَّمَاعُ <span class="c2">(فَزَحَلَ)</span> ـ بالحاء ـ!.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>